---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const title = "Affiliate disclosure · PetFoodRate";
const description = "How PetFoodRate is funded: affiliate links, full transparency, zero brand sponsorship on ratings. Independent A to E grades.";
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="legal-page">
    <header class="legal-header">
      <p class="eyebrow">Transparency</p>
      <h1>Affiliate disclosure</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        PetFoodRate is an independent pet food rating service. A to E grades are awarded without any financial counterpart from brands. To stay free, we occasionally use affiliate links. Here is exactly how it works.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>What is an affiliate link?</h2>
      <p>
        When you click a "View on Zooplus" button from PetFoodRate, you reach the partner store through a tracked link. If you buy in the following days, the store pays PetFoodRate a small commission (typically 3 to 8 % of the basket). You pay the exact same price as visiting directly. No surcharge.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Who are our partners?</h2>
      <p>As of 22 April 2026:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Zooplus FR</strong> · affiliate partner validated via the Awin network. Large catalogue (dog, cat, small pets, birds).</li>
        <li>Pending partners: Maxi Zoo FR, Just Russel FR, Edgard &amp; Cooper.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Only relevant products stocked by our partners show a "View on" button. Other pages remain purely informational.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Does affiliation influence ratings?</h2>
      <p>
        No. A to E scores are computed by our public methodology (analysed composition, sub-scores for proteins, nutrition, undesirables, transparency, species adaptability). No brand can "buy" a better grade. No affiliate partner has access to our rubrics before publication. Grades are never modified after a partnership is accepted.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>How to spot an affiliate link?</h2>
      <p>
        Every sponsored CTA is flagged: "Affiliate partner" badge, distinct green button, explicit affiliation mention. Links go through our <code>/go/{"{"}product-id{"}"}</code> redirect so we can measure clicks on our side. Links carry <code>rel="sponsored nofollow"</code> per Google guidelines.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Your rights as a user</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You can use PetFoodRate without ever clicking an affiliate link. All grades and analyses stay accessible.</li>
        <li>You can withdraw your consent for analytics cookies via the cookie banner (footer).</li>
        <li>Affiliate click data contains no personally identifiable information. We store: product id, partner, referrer, country, date.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-section">
      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        Write to <a href="mailto:contact@petfoodrate.com">contact@petfoodrate.com</a>. We reply within 48 hours on weekdays.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>

  <style>
    .legal-page {
      max-width: 44rem;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.25rem 5rem;
    }
    .legal-header {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #16a34a;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    }
    .legal-page h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin: 0 0 1rem;
    }
    .lede {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--text-muted, #475569);
      margin: 0;
    }
    .legal-section { margin-top: 2.25rem; }
    .legal-section h2 { font-size: 1.35rem; margin: 0 0 0.6rem; }
    .legal-section p { line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 0.75rem; }
    .legal-section ul { margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem 1.25rem; line-height: 1.65; }
    .legal-section code {
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.08);
      padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.92em;
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
